name bookmark
category Package
revision 79461
shortdesc A new bookmark (outline) organization for hyperref
longdesc This package implements a new bookmark (outline) organization
longdesc for package hyperref. Bookmark properties such as style and
longdesc color can now be set. Other action types are available (URI,
longdesc GoToR, Named). The bookmarks are generated in the first compile
longdesc run. Package hyperref uses two runs.
