name refcount
category Package
revision 79461
shortdesc Counter operations with label references
longdesc Provides commands \setcounterref and \addtocounterref which use
longdesc the section (or whatever) number from the reference as the
longdesc value to put into the counter, as in: ...\label{sec:foo} ...
longdesc \setcounterref{foonum}{sec:foo} Commands \setcounterpageref and
longdesc \addtocounterpageref do the corresponding thing with the page
longdesc reference of the label. No .ins file is distributed; process
longdesc the .dtx with plain TeX to create one.
